panies  that  come  from  other  countries  with  whom  we  are  allied  to 
try  to  bring  Iran,  for  example,  into  a  different  circumstance  with 
respect to nuclear production? 

Is  it  the  case  that  nuclear  weapons  production,  I  should  say,  is 
it  the  case  that  doing  business  with  Iran  by  any  of  these  corpora-

