not  be  able  to  go  back  into  that,  or  go  back  into  that  country  even 
under the current law. 

So, as it stands our decision to pull out of Iran was one that was 
made  with  the  understanding  of  the  consequences  that  the  law 
would  not  allow  us  to  go  back  in.  So,  the  current  law  would  not 
allow us to go back in. 

If  you  all  decide  to  change  the  law  in  some  way,  we  will  follow 

that law and continue to do so. 

