took  place 

from 

The  registered  Dubai  address  for  HPSL  was,  has  been,  and  remains  at  Al  Moosa 
Tower.  Since  1994,  HPSL  has  maintained  operations  facilities  in  the  following 
Dubai locations:

Nad Al Sheeba (office), Sheikh Rashid Plot, Dubai, UAE.
Al Quoz (storage location and cement-mixing plant), Al Quoz, Dubai, UAE.
Oilfield Supply Centre, B–15, Roundabout #8, Jebel Ali Free Zone, UAE.

The Al Moosa Tower address was never the operational home or address of HPSL. 
The  Al  Moosa  Tower  location  was  the  home,  for  some  period  of  time  of  a  branch 
office  of  Halliburton  Limited  (HL)  a  U.K.  corporation.  and  later  of  Halliburton 
Worldwide Limited (HWL), a company registered in the Cayman Islands. 
