Ms.  Williams  statement  during  the  hearing  was  as  follows:  (Page  14  of  the  com-
plete transcript provided to us, or page 53 of the partial transcript) ‘‘I think the in-
vestigation  is  ongoing.  We  have  responded  to  all  of  the  inquiries  from  the  Depart-
