and  end?  What  was  the  financial  value  of  these  contracts?  Which  economic  sector 
did  these  contracts  cover?  Which  U.S.  companies  were  subcontractors  to  these  con-
tracts? Which non-U.S. companies were subcontractors to these contracts?

